General.Name: Bukit Sembawang Estates Limited
General.Description: Bukit Sembawang Estates Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the property development and related activities in Singapore. The company operates in three segments: Property Development, Investment Holding, and Hospitality. It develops and sells residential properties; and holds and manages office buildings and investments. The company also owns and operates serviced apartment units. Bukit Sembawang Estates Limited was founded in 1911 and is based in Singapore.
